-- 2010-12-23T21:24:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-23/jets-to-make-game-time-decision-on-starting-injured-sanchez-ryan-says.html
Mark Sanchez’s injured throwing
shoulder is worse than originally thought and it will be a
“game time-type decision” if the New York Jets’ quarterback
plays against the Chicago Bears this weekend, coach Rex Ryan
said at a news conference today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
